cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.AR, cs.PF, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with optimizing work distribution on a heterogeneous computing system.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes using machine learning for evaluation of system performance.
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) is relevant as the paper describes a heterogeneous platform comprising of CPUs and a co-processor.
- cs.PF (Performance) is relevant as the paper aims to minimize overall application execution time.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper proposes a method for optimizing the system configuration.
